column5: A very nice report -- congrats on a geat day coupled with 2 exc trout --  might just start the fall brookie season next week myself
Awesome.  I love my float tube. Is that the older Cumberland? Mine has a nice 5 inch cushion seat,that keeps your butt out of the water.  Just enlarged the pic. Not a Cumberland.
That looks ridiculously fun, and probably a little more comfy than a canoe.
Wow !!! Nice fish ... The scenery looks amazing too !!! Cheers
Nice fish! I must get me a float tube.

Thanks for the comments guys. Yeah, my butt is in the water. Next time I purchase a float tube, I'll definitely buy one like the one that you have. I bought mine at Canadian tire 5 years ago when it was on a crazy sale. Regular price was 150$ and it was on sale for 50$. At that price I went ahead and purchased 2. This way, I always bring someone with me when I go float tubing.
Smashin brookies with the Abu Specialist! Nice work, great catch
nice job, wish we had more brookies closer to home for me
Wow, nice brooks man. They sure look like some nice healthy specimens
Was looking forward to your Brookie reports ... love your fish pics man .... keep'em coming
Thanks guys, next weekend I'll be out chasing brookies once again. Hopefully I hook into a few males that are sporting their gorgeous fall colours.
